{
  "stem": "13911.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, it's-- I don't know how the mind works.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It did not happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you're young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe if-- when you were old, you cannot say, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you're young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have your youth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, it's like a rosebud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is only a stem, and suddenly it's full blown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you're young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess this is the secret of love-- like-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Oh, boy, I'm making a fool of myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the secret of life, maybe, that, hey, suddenly there is a beautiful bloom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We started going into the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't even know or understand the language then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But live.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the sun was shining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was so warm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just like something-- after a horrible, horrible nightmare, suddenly, hey, it's beautiful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then again, you would like to understand, how could you stay on the German soil?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the first time, we were-- because the Germans did not know the difference.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They not like the Pole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He would just have to smell and know that you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German didn't know unless you told him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we would walk the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody would look at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I speak, and we spoke German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before you knew, I was reading German books.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I really was good at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and when we spoke, we didn't have to like, all-- all cringed, all-- all crumpled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, like, in Polish, Shh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't talk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't do it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because nobody knew who you are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if I spoke and they sensed, they detected an accent, they thought I'm Greek, I'm Italian, I'm anything but Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Berlin?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we stayed with-- we stayed nine months, actually, in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
